55.7	La_Scala	La Scala	La Scala (Italian: ), is a world renowned opera house in Milan, Italy. The theatre was inaugurated on 3 August 1778 and was originally known as the New Royal-Ducal Theatre at La Scala (Italian: ). The premiere performance was Antonio Salieri's Europa riconosciuta.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/52/Teatro_alla_Scala.gif/300px-Teatro_alla_Scala.gif
